69019.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
69019.description: It is the Day of Black Sun and the group meets up with the invasion force."The day has finally arrived and Aang is ready to take on the Fire Lord. But they soon realize that things aren't going to go according to plan, and their surprise attack isn't so unexpected." Part 2 is "The Day of Black Sun, Part 2: The Eclipse."

69020.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
69020.description: Second part to "The Day of Black Sun, Part 1: The Invasion". The eclipse has started and the gang only has a few minutes to get into an underground bunker and find and defeat Ozai. Zuko confront his father and learn about his mother's banishment while Aang, Sokka and Toph fight Azula and her Dai Li agents.

69021.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
69021.description: Mr. Krabs finds out that Plankton's afraid of whales. // Gary falls for a snail named Mary.

69022.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
69022.description: Mr. Krab opens a Dinner Theater at the Krusty Krab. // SpongeBob takes his pals to Texas to see Sandy in a squirrel rodeo.

69023.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
69023.description: Karai is brainwashed and starts hunting the Turtles.

69024.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
69024.description: The Turtles get whisked through time by apprentice Time Master Renet, and they must all work together to defeat the evil Time Master Savanti Romero.

69025.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
69025.description: When Temutai kidnaps a kung fu master, Shifu turns to Po for help.

69026.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
69026.description: Po discovers his dad, Mr. Ping, is dating Scorpion, but he has trouble trusting his former enemy who claims to no longer be evil.

69027.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
69027.description: Marlene goes over to meet the newest zoo animal, and she mysteriously disappears. The penguins and lemurs attempt to rescue her, but they are taken, too. All except for Kowalski, the last penguin standing. // When Julien is taken to the zoo infirmary for acting even weirder than usual, Maurice is left in charge. Everything goes smoothly, until suddenly Maurice is acting even crazier than Julien ever did.

69028.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
69028.description: The penguins and lemurs face off in a race. The penguins in a souped-up version of their car and the lemurs in Alice's zoo cart. Winner takes the loser's car! // Alice gives Rico a tummy-settling medicine just after he swallows a ticking time bomb.

69029.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
69029.description: When Squidward gets spritzed with plant growth spray, he becomes monstrously huge. // When Patrick realizes that he is the only one out of all his friends without a nose, he decides he needs to get a nose, too.

69030.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
69030.description: It's time to restock the secret Krabby Patty ingredient, and it is SpongeBob's duty to make sure the ingredient is delivered safely to the Krusty Krab. // Plankton has a customer who eats at the Chum Bucket every day.

69031.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
69031.description: In an attempt to get away from SpongeBob, Squidward drives off in his boat as fast as he can, but he is pulled over and ordered to go to boating school. // Mr. Krabs decides to go into the tabloid business.

69032.title: Nella The Princess Knight
69032.description: When Sir Coach embarks on a dangerous quest, Nella tags along and realizes she still has a lot to learn. // Nella helps Smelgly the dragon fulfill her dream of joining the Knight Brigade.

69033.title: Nella The Princess Knight
69033.description: Trinket is desperate to keep things perfect for Royal Family Picture Day. // Nella and Norma's 'Best Sisters' playdate is interrupted by two arguing rock giant brothers.

69034.title: Bubble Guppies
69034.description: The Bubble Guppies are going on a camping trip! Grab your flashlights and gather around the campfire to make s'mores and hear about the spooky legend of Pinkfoot!

69035.title: Bubble Guppies
69035.description: Gil wants to adopt a puppy! But before he can bring the puppy home, the Bubble Guppies must learn how to take care of pets.

69036.title: Dora the Explorer
69036.description: Dora and Boots read about a chicken that's as big as a house and set off to meet him.

69037.title: Dora the Explorer
69037.description: Dora and Boots must reunite a baby blue bird with her mother.

69038.title: Rusty Rivets
69038.description: Frankie Fritz challenges Rusty and Ruby to a race around Sparkton Hills, with the Mobile Rivet Lab as the stakes. // Rusty and Ruby try to save the school's art fair from being frozen over by Frankie Fritz and his Skunk-bot, Frankford.

69039.title: Rusty Rivets
69039.description: Rusty and Ruby set off on their pirate ship in a hunt for a buried treasure. // When Frankie's robo-mouse accidentally gets copied dozens of times, it's up to Rusty and Ruby to round up the little critters before they take over Sparkton Hills.

69040.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
69040.description: When Crusher tries to cheat at a carnival game, he accidentally strands himself and Pickle on a giant rocket! Now it’s up to Blaze and AJ to rescue the two trucks before their runaway rocket crashes into the garbage dump.

69041.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
69041.description: Gabby, Blaze and AJ are out in the wilderness when they get a call, Blaze's friends have come down with a sickness called the Sneezles! Our heroes must race back to Axle City to bring the sick trucks the medicine oil they need.

69042.title: PAW Patrol
69042.description: The pups are learning the ancient art of Pup-Fu! They'll need it to get back Sensei Farmer Yumi's ancient martial arts scroll, after Mayor Humdinger's Kit-tastrophe Crew use their Cat-Jitsu skills to steal it!

69043.title: PAW Patrol
69043.description: It’s the annual Mayor’s Race, and Mayor Humdinger is planning his most devious cheating scheme yet. // When Ryder comes across a map for buried treasure, Mayor Humdinger snatches the map and runs off to find the loot for himself.

69044.title: PAW Patrol
69044.description: The PAW Patrol plan a special celebration for Wally the Walrus. When he doesn't show up, they find he has a special new friend named Walinda! // During Cap’n Turbot's archaeological dig, a rock slide unearths a big dinosaur bone!

69045.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
69045.description: It is prehistoric Bikini Bottom, and we spend a day in the life of SpongeGar, Patar, and Squog. Thanks to the magic of an underwater thunderstorm, our three Neanderthal friends discover fire.

69046.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
69046.description: SpongeBob and Patrick turn SpongeBob’s house into an indoor miniature golf course! // When SpongeBob realizes how many memories are attached to all of his possessions, he is reluctant to throw anything way.

69047.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
69047.description: Mr. Krabs refuses to let SpongeBob throw away a moldy Krabby Patty that was festering under the grill. He tries to pawn it off on customers to save the fifty-two cents he would have lost if he threw the patty away. // SpongeBob, while sand sledding, breaks his butt! Paranoid for his own safety he becomes a hermit and cloisters himself in his house. Sandy and Patrick do all they can to try and get him to come out, but to no avail.

69048.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
69048.description: Kowalski has a rival, if you even can call it a rivalry. A Delaware Blue Hen has taken up residence at the zoo, and she has the amazing ability to predict the future! Kowalski doesn't buy the psychic chicken hype and sets out to discredit her. The truth turns out to be far more sinister than a simple sports-pickin' chicken, and Kowalski will have to use all his best moves to wiggle out of this mess. Thumb Drive: The penguins need a thumb, and Maurice's fits the bill nicely. Using the opposable digit thumbprint to break into a secret weapons lab gets the penguins all atwitter. King Julien is unhappy that his right hand man is running around on missions with the birds so he sets out to sabotage the mission. As with most of King Julien's plans, this scheme turns out to be "thumbs down"!

69049.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
69049.description: Private's in heaven - icy, freezing heaven. The Lunacorns on Ice extravaganza is in town, and Skipper's determined to take him as a treat. Accompanied by unexpected fellow fanboys Bing and Roy, the gang heads to the arena. Things get a bit d-icey when the gorilla and rhino end up on the ice with the lunacorns. The enraged director is ready to shutter the whole thing unless they find some way to slip 'n slide out of it. Showdown on Fairway 18:A legendary putter is at the center of controversy when the Amarillo Kid returns to the zoo. The slippery armadillo needs Private's help to make good on an ill-advised bet with two gopher brothers. Who's the bad guy here though? The gophers show up at the zoo to actually warn the penguins about the kid! The story takes us on more twists and turns than a Pebble Beach golf hole!

69050.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
69050.description: When Mantis returns to his hometown claiming to be the Dragon Warrior to impress his ex-fiancé, Po pretends to be his sidekick who doesn't know kung fu.

69051.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
69051.description: Shifu tells the citizens of the Valley of Peace that whoever can defeat Po before sunset will become the new Dragon Warrior. When Hundun hears of the challenge, he returns to the village to claim the title.

69052.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
69052.description: When Donnie upgrades Metalhead's artificial intelligence, he must decide if he can trust a sentient Metalhead or if he has created a new foe.

69053.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
69053.description: When the Rat King returns, Splinter must overcome his guilt and fear of the Rat King controlling his mind in order to defeat his foe once and for all.

69054.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
69054.description: SpongeBob can't drive, but you don't need a license to operate a self-driving car! // Patrick thinks he's an old man, so it's up to SpongeBob to remind him how much fun being a kid can be!

69055.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
69055.description: SpongeBob and Patrick exchange tiny living versions of themselves. It's a whole hunk of homunculus fun! // Plankton tells his Grandma that he owns the Krusty Krab, but must keep the lie going when she comes to visit.

69056.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
69056.description: SpongeBob and Patrick become trapped in an alternate dimension where anything they draw comes to life. // SpongeBob and Patrick help Bubble Bass move out of his mother's basement.

69057.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
69057.description: Po realizes he must select a trophy for the Hall of Heroes, but instead finds himself helping a young villager retrieve a rabbit doll that is much more important than it looks.

69058.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
69058.description: Po disguises himself as the merciless villain, Tong Fo, to try and locate a hidden weapon.

69059.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
69059.description: As the zoo starts feeding them imitation fish cakes, the penguins take matters into their own flippers and hatch a plan to hijack a fish delivery truck. // During a particularly cold day, the rats show up and challenge the penguins to a hockey match.

69060.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
69060.description: As the vet gathers the penguins to give them a shot, Skipper's fear of needles takes over and he goes on the run. // During a solar eclipse, Phil and Mason convince the bossy Julien that the sky spirits are angry at him. He starts acting extra-nice.

69061.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
69061.description: The Turtles are accidentally transported to the past, and they cross paths with a familiar ninja clan.

69062.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
69062.description: Leo decides to sneak into Shredder's Lair alone only to face the biggest mutant threat yet.

69063.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
69063.description: In order to increase profits, Krabs decides that the Krusty Krab will now be open 24 hours a day. He orders SpongeBob and Squidward to work all night - what's known as the Graveyard Shift. // Ms. Puff pays a visit to the Krusty Krab and Mr. Krabs is instantly smitten with her. He recruits SpongeBob to help him woo Ms. Puff. SpongeBob tries to play match maker, but he screws it all up and Krabs threatens his job!

69064.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
69064.description: Spongebob has an assignment for boating school. He must write an 800 word essay before the next morning. Spongebob starts to write it, but he gets distracted easily and can't keep his mind on his work. // When Patrick's parents come over for Starfish Day, Patrick gets upset that they still think he isn't very smart. Spongebob offers to act stupid next to Pat in front of Patricks' parents in order to make Pat look smarter.

69065.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
69065.description: SpongeBob reads a "bad" word off the dumpster behind the Krusty Krabs and he doesn't know what it means. He asks Pat who explains to him that it's a fancy word and both of them start using it in every sentence they can. // When eager Spongebob enrolls in Squidward's community art class, arrogant Squidward attempts to teach Spongebob strictly by the book.

69066.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
69066.description: When Taotie tries to destroy the Jade Palace and fails, he is sent to prison while his son, Bian Zao, is left behind with Po, who acts like a big brother to the boy who thinks everything is lame!

69067.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
69067.description: While repairs are being made to the noodle shop, Mr. Ping turns the training hall into a restaurant!

69068.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
69068.description: Mort is exposed to Kowalski's super-ray, and he grows super-big and strong. // Marlene gets a new roommate! At first, she's excited to have a new best friend. But her attitude changes when her roommate turns out to have some pretty disgusting habits.

69069.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
69069.description: The rats have been terrorizing Roger the alligator. He asks the penguins for help. Their solution: swap Roger's brain with Rico's, and let the but kicking begin! // A robot is sent to the zoo to learn the habits of lemurs before it's sent into space.

69070.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
69070.description: The gang leaves the Fire Nation, humbled and embarrassed by the failure of the invasion. They head to the Western Air Temple. However, unknown to them, Zuko is also following them in the hope of joining their group to teach Aang firebending.

69071.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
69071.description: Aang is ready to start his firebending training. However, as Zuko attempts to teach him, he realizes he has lost all his firebending power; as he is no longer drawing his firebending power from rage, anger and his desire to capture Aang. They journey to find the true source of firebending.

69072.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
69072.description: When money hungry Mr. Krabs discovers that customers love Spongebob's special jellyfish jelly Krabby Patty, he convinces Spongebob to bring him as many of the jellyfish as he can. // Krabs enters SpongeBob in the athletic competition - the Fry Cook Games. SpongeBob is thrilled and starts to train hard. When Pat wants to train as well, SpongeBob tells him you have to be a fry cook to compete.

69073.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
69073.description: Believing Mr. Krab is taking advantage, Squidward convinces na´ve Spongebob to join with him and threaten to a strike. When Mr. Krabs fires them both, a frustrated Squidward tries to teach Spongebob the art of picketing. // A large worm is terrorizing Bikini Bottom and SpongeBob is terrified of it. Sandy thinks he is a chicken and drags him out into the wilderness to take the worm on. When they finally see the worm, it turns out SpongeBob was right.

69074.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
69074.description: Plankton has a new invention that allows him to switch lives with Mr. Krabs. He is so excited because once he has Mr. Krabs' life, he will also have the Krabby Patty secret formula. // When Larry the Lobster is short one man for lifeguard duty, SpongeBob volunteers. Larry describes all the perks of the jobs: tanning, the whistle, the attention. What SpongeBob doesn't get is that you have to be able to swim.

69075.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
69075.description: After an accident, Donnie finds himself slowly losing his intelligence.

69076.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
69076.description: The Turtles are baited by an unknown enemy into deadly traps.

69077.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
69077.description: When Shifu's con-man father comes back into town, Po finds himself in the middle.

69078.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
69078.description: Po is excited when he discovers a kung fu prodigy, but starts to worry when people seem to prefer the new kid to their beloved Dragon Warrior.

69079.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
69079.description: When the penguins bring Marlene with them on a sno-cone mission in the park, she can't handle the freedom of being outside the zoo walls. // Max the cat is on the run from evil animal control Officer X, and he comes to the penguins for help.

69080.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
69080.description: When Rico gets a freaky fortune from his cookie, he initially ignores it. Julien sets out to make Rico's fortune come true. // A female chimp named Lulu arrives at the zoo for a short stay, and Phil is smitten. Unfortunately, Lulu falls for Mason.

69081.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
69081.description: On watch-duty, Private sees a terrifying Skorka: a sky orca whale. No one believes it exists, so Private sets out to battle the Sorka on his own. // When the penguins are interrupted mid-operation by a nosey scientist, they leave the zoo in danger.

69082.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
69082.description: SpongeBob and Patrick build a small clubhouse in a tree and get inside. When Squid comes by they tell him he can't join the club because he wouldn't fit in. Upset, Squid insists on joining and climbs the tree and gets inside. // SpongeBob finds a stray sea horse and adopts it. When it comes time to go to work, SpongeBob can't bear to leave him at home so he takes him to work and hides him in the kitchen.

69083.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
69083.description: When SpongeBob learns that Squid has never actually tried a Krabby Patty, he becomes obsessed with the idea that Squid must try it. // There is a new bully in boating school named Flats who threatens to beat SpongeBob up after school. SpongeBob is terrified and tries to get help, but everyone is under Flats terror hold already

75394.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
75394.description: SpongeBob and Patrick dig a tunnel between their two houses and drive Squidward nuts. // Pat learns just enough karate to wreak havoc in Bikini Bottom.
